spec_data.Name: perl-CGI-Application-Plugin-ViewCode
spec_data.Description:
This plugin works by adding extra run modes (named view_code and view_pod)
to the application. By calling this run mode you can see the source or POD
of the running module (by default) or you can specify which module you
would like to view.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:00:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Allows you to view the source of a CGI::Application module
